{"tid":2120734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法庭文件：被起訴共軍女軍醫躲在中国駐舊金山領館","createTime":"2020-07-23T01:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T14:54:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":314,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"07cb0219dbe5efd3be973eef1906e5dde4c05fdd","tid":2120734,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:01:03.000Z","msg":"聯邦檢察官遞交的一份法庭文件顯示，一名隱瞞在中國一所軍醫大學真實身份的科研人員在6月20日因簽證欺詐問題接受聯邦調查局面談之後，躲進了中國駐加利福尼亞州舊金山（三藩市）的領事館。<br />\n<br />\n這份7月20日在加利福尼亞北區聯邦法庭提交的文件中說，唐娟（Juan Tang，譯音）以J-1訪問學者簽證在加州大學戴維斯分校軍事研究工作，她在申請簽證時沒有披露她與中國人民解放軍的關係，調查發現她為空軍軍醫大學工作，是現役軍人...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/san-franciso-consulate-harbors-a-chinese-military-researcher-20200722/5514137.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fsan-franciso-consulate-harbors-a-chinese-military-researcher-20200722%2F5514137.html&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgP3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=6e267a04\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/san-franciso-consulate-harbors-a-chinese-military-researcher-20200722/5514137.html</a>"},{"pid":"4c103043f155611964aa21592fd13e2604e1003c","tid":2120734,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:02:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0076455f016aa1642c63564df0f2a7d099005bf","tid":2120734,"uid":212509,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:03:26.000Z","msg":"拉人封舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58b758103ff2d07833e3fd740a4439b30d63592","tid":2120734,"uid":19552,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:04:24.000Z","msg":"個個爭住篤灰"},{"pid":"f4e834885eafb9595bbc85ff375e805676736a60","tid":2120734,"uid":19552,"like":107,"dislike":1,"score":106,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T01:05:05.000Z","msg":"美國開放 篤大灰有綠卡 條隊應該夠橫越大西洋"},{"pid":"1d4bb2ff18d2db6c5810a6f2c4b58d2537